ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS in order to (1) permit the Government to assume a greater oversight role over the body designated to govern immigration consultants (2) protect potential temporary and permanent resident applicants and refugee claimants (3) balance the applicant's and the representative's privacy interests with the need to maintain the integrity of the process.
